{"title":"黑河歌——塞北牧歌之一","authors":["巴牧"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":4,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑河歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——塞北牧歌之一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴牧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未尝黑河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先听黑河歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑河过去多荒凉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野草丛生鸟扎窝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地闲无人种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水甜无人喝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说塞外满天沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春来不见花一朵……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未尝黑河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又听黑河歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今黑河开颜笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满河欢乐满岸歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地是翡翠地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河是金银河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林就像遮天伞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水上船穿梭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日黑河放光采，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕儿伸翅戏水波，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片红花塞外开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美似江南河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春忙播种秋忙收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一河甜水幸福多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜来岸上千家灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家欢唱黑河歌。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}